<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA611_06_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema611_06.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema611_06_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" class="fraction_box_title" lang="y">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              <div class="mixed_fraction ml_0">
                2
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              ÷5를 두 가지 방법으로 계산하고, 비교해 봅시다.
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">대분수를 가분수로 바꾸어 지원이와 도훈이의 방법으로 계산해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="input_area">
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_06_SU/0004_content1.png" alt="">

            <div class="txt" lang="y">
              분자가 자연수의<br>
              배수인 분수로 바꾸어<br> 
              계산해 볼까?
            </div>

            <div class="name" lang="y">지원</div>

            <div class="equation">
              <span>2</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>3</span>
              </div>
              <span>÷5=</span>
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap up">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>3</span>
              </span>
              <span>÷5=</span>
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap up">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="35"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>15</span>
              </span>
              <span>÷5=</span>
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap up">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="35"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span>÷5</span>
                </span>
                <span>15</span>
              </span>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="(7)/(15)" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">대분수를 가분수로 바꾸어 지원이와 도훈이의 방법으로 계산해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="input_area">
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_06_SU/0004_content2.png" alt="">

            <div class="txt" lang="y">
              분수의 곱셈으로<br>
              나타내어 계산해 볼까?
            </div>

            <div class="name" lang="y">도훈</div>

            <div class="equation">
              <span>2</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>3</span>
              </div>
              <span>÷5=</span>
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap up">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="7"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>3</span>
              </span>
              <span>÷5=</span>
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span>7</span>
                <span>3</span>
              </span>
              <span>×</span>
              <span class="fraction_box">
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap up">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
                <span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="5"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </span>
              </span>
              <span>=</span>
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="(7)/(15)" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3 lang="y">
            <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
              <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                <div class="mixed_fraction ml_0">
                  2
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <span>3</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                ÷5를 계산한 방법을 비교하여 이야기해 보세요.
              </div>
            </div>
          </h3>

          <div class="input_wrap">
            <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
            <div class="example_box">
              <p lang="y">둘 다 대분수를 가분수로 바꾼 후 계산하였지만 지원이는 분자가 자연수의 배수인 분수로 바꾸어 계산했고, 도훈이는 분수의 곱셈으로 나타내어 계산했습니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
